  "content": "<h2>1 先说说我制作的 SuperMemo 懒人包是如何做到图片保存的：</h2><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-5218a57265f7f2b160cca0033d018176_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"889\" data-rawheight=\"556\" data-original-token=\"v2-5218a57265f7f2b160cca0033d018176\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-0e018a55c43152a7a32766872c54564f_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"889\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-5218a57265f7f2b160cca0033d018176_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;889&#39; height=&#39;556&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"889\" data-rawheight=\"556\" data-original-token=\"v2-5218a57265f7f2b160cca0033d018176\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-0e018a55c43152a7a32766872c54564f_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"889\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-5218a57265f7f2b160cca0033d018176_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-5218a57265f7f2b160cca0033d018176_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"eYATsAOx\">在这个页面，按下快捷键 Ctrl+F9，可以查看这张卡片的源文件：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-5b2f6f8a6b31e794f40072ae1618e4df_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"784\" data-rawheight=\"447\" data-original-token=\"v2-5b2f6f8a6b31e794f40072ae1618e4df\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-e3b9e4f88c7c16054738641710439066_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"784\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-5b2f6f8a6b31e794f40072ae1618e4df_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;784&#39; height=&#39;447&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"784\" data-rawheight=\"447\" data-original-token=\"v2-5b2f6f8a6b31e794f40072ae1618e4df\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-e3b9e4f88c7c16054738641710439066_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"784\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-5b2f6f8a6b31e794f40072ae1618e4df_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-5b2f6f8a6b31e794f40072ae1618e4df_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-text\">file:///[PrimaryStorage]5.jpg</code></pre></div><p data-pid=\"N4ex87Tn\">就是这张图片的相对路径，[PrimaryStorage] 对应的是 SuperMemo 存储卡片的路径 /sm18/systems/{集合名称}/elements/</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-486fc9650a6f225bfc16343168e4ec49_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"983\" data-rawheight=\"436\" data-original-token=\"v2-486fc9650a6f225bfc16343168e4ec49\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-b9fe37880a0c5b9e9aaaa9009867c000_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"983\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-486fc9650a6f225bfc16343168e4ec49_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;983&#39; height=&#39;436&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"983\" data-rawheight=\"436\" data-original-token=\"v2-486fc9650a6f225bfc16343168e4ec49\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-b9fe37880a0c5b9e9aaaa9009867c000_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"983\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-486fc9650a6f225bfc16343168e4ec49_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-486fc9650a6f225bfc16343168e4ec49_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"joihpWZG\">所以这种路径在任何人、任何电脑上都可以找到正确的图片位置。</p><h2>2 粘贴多图，这个要么从网页，要么从 wps、word 等软件里面复制过去</h2><p data-pid=\"O7fm-Vs7\">如果是网页，那就简单，本地化图片就行了。如果是 wps、word 等软件复制过去，由于这种复制所带的图片路径是其他软件自己的路径，所以换电脑、删文件后，图片就会丢失。目前没有什么好的解决方案，我只能建议一张一张复制。</p><h2>3 我一般用截图+粘贴，或者是网络图片+本地化</h2><p data-pid=\"enDbg2V8\">不过这个需要 Quicker 动作辅助一下</p><p data-pid=\"2hUdvCIW\">截图+粘贴后，效果应该是这样的：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-bf48c90a3a12bb5e59d06bf4ff85e676_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"978\" data-rawheight=\"524\" data-original-token=\"v2-bf48c90a3a12bb5e59d06bf4ff85e676\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-16633117030118079ed0feb44f5b054f_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"978\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-bf48c90a3a12bb5e59d06bf4ff85e676_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;978&#39; height=&#39;524&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"978\" data-rawheight=\"524\" data-original-token=\"v2-bf48c90a3a12bb5e59d06bf4ff85e676\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-16633117030118079ed0feb44f5b054f_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"978\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-bf48c90a3a12bb5e59d06bf4ff85e676_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-bf48c90a3a12bb5e59d06bf4ff85e676_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"r5_Bbqaz\">按 ctrl + F9 看看源文件：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-b5e12d59f2680fdab95fa3bc4c6ecfb6_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"804\" data-rawheight=\"221\" data-original-token=\"v2-b5e12d59f2680fdab95fa3bc4c6ecfb6\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-63c15c7c1112833518e9e386b0afc657_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"804\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-b5e12d59f2680fdab95fa3bc4c6ecfb6_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;804&#39; height=&#39;221&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"804\" data-rawheight=\"221\" data-original-token=\"v2-b5e12d59f2680fdab95fa3bc4c6ecfb6\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-63c15c7c1112833518e9e386b0afc657_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"804\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-b5e12d59f2680fdab95fa3bc4c6ecfb6_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-b5e12d59f2680fdab95fa3bc4c6ecfb6_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"5Fz6ybfg\">这个 file:///z:/applications%20(parallels)/sm18-lazy-package/sm18/systems/abc%20of%20supermemo%2018/elements/22/229.jpg 一看就知道是绝对路径，如果移动 sm18 的位置，图片就显示不出来了。但是我的 Quicker 动作：</p><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//getquicker.net/Sharedaction%3Fcode%3D859bda04-fe78-4385-1b37-08d88a0dba1c\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">统一格式</a><p data-pid=\"Z1MsVp_d\">在统一格式的时候，进行了一个文本替换操作：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-e6f2383728a46b773fde4461b90cab79_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"799\" data-rawheight=\"564\" data-original-token=\"v2-e6f2383728a46b773fde4461b90cab79\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-bf620ce1280149ab2c35265a50430186_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"799\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-e6f2383728a46b773fde4461b90cab79_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;799&#39; height=&#39;564&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"799\" data-rawheight=\"564\" data-original-token=\"v2-e6f2383728a46b773fde4461b90cab79\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-bf620ce1280149ab2c35265a50430186_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"799\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-e6f2383728a46b773fde4461b90cab79_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-e6f2383728a46b773fde4461b90cab79_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"lmhGraJ_\">所以，对着有图片的卡片使用这个 Quicker 动作，会自动把绝对路径替换成相对路径：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-753e1e8b4790e03f234aea88d8b06e03_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"786\" data-rawheight=\"702\" data-original-token=\"v2-753e1e8b4790e03f234aea88d8b06e03\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-eaff0acba54839e86893f5c285da7ebc_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"786\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-753e1e8b4790e03f234aea88d8b06e03_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;786&#39; height=&#39;702&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"786\" data-rawheight=\"702\" data-original-token=\"v2-753e1e8b4790e03f234aea88d8b06e03\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-eaff0acba54839e86893f5c285da7ebc_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"786\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-753e1e8b4790e03f234aea88d8b06e03_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-753e1e8b4790e03f234aea88d8b06e03_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"QiKl3JjJ\">然后随便调整 sm18 的位置，图片也不会丢了。</p><h2>4 对图床了解不多，我认知中的图床就是网络图片</h2><h2>5 你说得对</h2><h2>6 就是把图片存放在和卡片源文件同一个目录下</h2><p data-pid=\"Wy1jZ-wS\">supermemo 自己是没有统一变更图片路径的功能，但是这一点可以用 vscode 做到：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-c4a94c515c4cb65da4d217ccae9c9f1d_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1919\" data-rawheight=\"675\" data-original-token=\"v2-c4a94c515c4cb65da4d217ccae9c9f1d\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-a11d63ec6b64bfe9a26e0c992ef4eb89_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1919\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-c4a94c515c4cb65da4d217ccae9c9f1d_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1919&#39; height=&#39;675&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1919\" data-rawheight=\"675\" data-original-token=\"v2-c4a94c515c4cb65da4d217ccae9c9f1d\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-a11d63ec6b64bfe9a26e0c992ef4eb89_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1919\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-c4a94c515c4cb65da4d217ccae9c9f1d_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-c4a94c515c4cb65da4d217ccae9c9f1d_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"1CaOnY5a\">简单来说，就是用 vscode 打开你的 sm18 文件夹</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-2eafb14c32f6267290e7bed233df3e32_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"366\" data-rawheight=\"255\" data-original-token=\"v2-2eafb14c32f6267290e7bed233df3e32\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-ba2a491af87f7ee4aa08e42cf820f643_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"content_image\" width=\"366\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;366&#39; height=&#39;255&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"366\" data-rawheight=\"255\" data-original-token=\"v2-2eafb14c32f6267290e7bed233df3e32\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-ba2a491af87f7ee4aa08e42cf820f643_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"content_image lazy\" width=\"366\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-2eafb14c32f6267290e7bed233df3e32_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"8wFzkBE7\">然后使用搜索替换功能（搜索 src=&#34;file:///.*?elements/，替换 src=&#34;file:///[PrimaryStorage]） </p><p data-pid=\"Mr5YNl88\">PS: 记得开正则替换，就是搜索框最右边那个 .* 的按钮</p><p data-pid=\"2MnHZqt-\">点一下全部替换就完事了 </p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-cd1da4d14d5181756e1885e2007a35f1_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"572\" data-rawheight=\"307\" data-original-token=\"v2-cd1da4d14d5181756e1885e2007a35f1\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-f4fc6ad53949735f3f83cb59f7cb0022_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"572\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-cd1da4d14d5181756e1885e2007a35f1_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;572&#39; height=&#39;307&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"572\" data-rawheight=\"307\" data-original-token=\"v2-cd1da4d14d5181756e1885e2007a35f1\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-f4fc6ad53949735f3f83cb59f7cb0022_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"572\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-cd1da4d14d5181756e1885e2007a35f1_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-cd1da4d14d5181756e1885e2007a35f1_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><h2>7 file:///[PrimaryStorage]xxx 就是相对路径</h2><h2>8 我也不知道</h2><h2>9 可以用图片</h2><p data-pid=\"6q7x0nZi\">但是图片修改起来很麻烦，我经常要修改卡片的措辞，图片上的文字你在 10 秒内改一下试试？</p><h2>10 截图+粘贴 or 网络图片+本地化</h2><p data-pid=\"LI5FC02h\">ctrl+f8，然后勾选你要本地化的网络图片，点一下 localize 就行了</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-9ff5ec99d220a832503109dd10558432_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"557\" data-rawheight=\"519\" data-original-token=\"v2-9ff5ec99d220a832503109dd10558432\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-1e3827f73f3c1606418fb6d3248bf570_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"557\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-9ff5ec99d220a832503109dd10558432_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;557&#39; height=&#39;519&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"557\" data-rawheight=\"519\" data-original-token=\"v2-9ff5ec99d220a832503109dd10558432\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-1e3827f73f3c1606418fb6d3248bf570_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"557\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-9ff5ec99d220a832503109dd10558432_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-9ff5ec99d220a832503109dd10558432_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-9d40b197f0f371a254994dfed7e7c5a1_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"717\" data-rawheight=\"636\" data-original-token=\"v2-9d40b197f0f371a254994dfed7e7c5a1\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-79e700c901408291c9b8cad903011196_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"717\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-9d40b197f0f371a254994dfed7e7c5a1_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;717&#39; height=&#39;636&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"717\" data-rawheight=\"636\" data-original-token=\"v2-9d40b197f0f371a254994dfed7e7c5a1\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-79e700c901408291c9b8cad903011196_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"717\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-9d40b197f0f371a254994dfed7e7c5a1_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-9d40b197f0f371a254994dfed7e7c5a1_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"Z_ABawxj\">然后使用我的统一格式动作就完事了。</p><h2>11 有帮助到你就好</h2>",
